(695, 'ASUS AM4 TUF Gaming X570-Plus (Wi-Fi) ATX Motherboard', 'ASUS AM4 TUF Gaming X570-Plus (Wi-Fi) ATX Motherboard', '<p>The&nbsp;<strong>ASUS TUF GAMING X570-PLUS (Wi-Fi) AM4 ATX Motherboard</strong>&nbsp;is built on the AMD X570 chipset supporting second- and third-generation AMD Ryzen processors with an AM4 socket. It has four memory slots for up to 128GB of dual-channel DDR4 RAM, which can run up to 4400 MHz when overclocked. For storage, it&#39;s equipped with eight SATA III ports and two 22110 M.2 slots. There are two PCIe 4.0 x16 slots for graphics cards, which can run at x16/x4 when both slots are filled, and another two PCIe 4.0 x1 slots for other PCI-based hardware. Other integrated features include Intel AC 9260 Wi-Fi 5, Realtek L8200A Gigabit LAN, and Realtek ALC S1200A 8-channel HD audio.</p>\n', '', 'asus-am4-tuf-gaming-x570-plus-wi-fi-atx-motherboard', 6, 103, '0', '0', 45, '<p>The&nbsp;<strong>ASUS TUF GAMING X570-PLUS (Wi-Fi) AM4 ATX Motherboard</strong>&nbsp;is built on the AMD X570 chipset supporting second- and third-generation AMD Ryzen processors with an AM4 socket. It has four memory slots for up to 128GB of dual-channel DDR4 RAM, which can run up to 4400 MHz when overclocked. For storage, it&#39;s equipped with eight SATA III ports and two 22110 M.2 slots. There are two PCIe 4.0 x16 slots for graphics cards, which can run at x16/x4 when both slots are filled, and another two PCIe 4.0 x1 slots for other PCI-based hardware. Other integrated features include Intel AC 9260 Wi-Fi 5, Realtek L8200A Gigabit LAN, and Realtek ALC S1200A 8-channel HD audio.</p>\n', '', 'featured,new,hot,day', NULL, 'en', 'nOFpzIR5H9QYLS1TUBqsyNf87', 0, '', '', '', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', '2020-07-08 07:16:21', '2020-07-08 07:16:21'),
