(709, 'ZOTAC GeForce GTX 1660 Ti 6GB GDDR6 Gaming Graphics Card', 'ZOTAC GeForce GTX 1660 Ti 6GB GDDR6 Gaming Graphics Card', '<ul>\n	<li>The New GeForce super compact 1660 Ti graphics card takes advantage of the NVIDIA Turing architecture and comes paired with GDDR6 ultra-fast memory to immerse you in incredible realism and brilliant performance in latest games.</li>\n	<li>GTX 1660 Ti comes with &lsquo;1536 CUDA cores&rsquo; and operates across a 192-bit wide bus interface with memory clock speed of 12 Gbps. It is a super compact card which ensures compatibility with 99 percent of systems. It also supports Engine Boost speeds up-to 1770 MHz.</li>\n	<li>A specially designed &lsquo;Wide array aluminum heatsink&rsquo; with direct copper contact paired with twin Fans enables a natural even heat distribution from the center core to the outer edges for efficient cooling.</li>\n	<li>It comes with 3 x Display port 1.4, 1 x HDMI 2.0b with support for 4K. It is also VR Ready. It is HDCP compliant and you can connect multiple displays (Up-to 4 simultaneously). The graphics card needs a power supply rated at at-least 450W.</li>\n	<li>It supports Microsoft Direct X 12 API, Vulkan API and OpenGL 4.5. It is fully compatible with Microsoft Windows 10/7 x64. It is fully compatible with NVIDIA Ansel and compatible with NVIDIA G-SYNC.</li>\n</ul>\n', '', 'zotac-geforce-gtx-1660-ti-6gb-gddr6-gaming-graphics-card', 6, 104, '0', '0', 48, '<ul>\n	<li>The New GeForce super compact 1660 Ti graphics card takes advantage of the NVIDIA Turing architecture and comes paired with GDDR6 ultra-fast memory to immerse you in incredible realism and brilliant performance in latest games.</li>\n	<li>GTX 1660 Ti comes with &lsquo;1536 CUDA cores&rsquo; and operates across a 192-bit wide bus interface with memory clock speed of 12 Gbps. It is a super compact card which ensures compatibility with 99 percent of systems. It also supports Engine Boost speeds up-to 1770 MHz.</li>\n	<li>A specially designed &lsquo;Wide array aluminum heatsink&rsquo; with direct copper contact paired with twin Fans enables a natural even heat distribution from the center core to the outer edges for efficient cooling.</li>\n	<li>It comes with 3 x Display port 1.4, 1 x HDMI 2.0b with support for 4K. It is also VR Ready. It is HDCP compliant and you can connect multiple displays (Up-to 4 simultaneously). The graphics card needs a power supply rated at at-least 450W.</li>\n	<li>It supports Microsoft Direct X 12 API, Vulkan API and OpenGL 4.5. It is fully compatible with Microsoft Windows 10/7 x64. It is fully compatible with NVIDIA Ansel and compatible with NVIDIA G-SYNC.</li>\n</ul>\n', '', 'featured,new,hot,day', NULL, 'en', 'HSmRdQYlqkBKjyvwhT3a51Vi2', 0, '', '', '', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', '2020-07-08 07:16:21', '2020-07-08 07:16:21'),
