(724, 'ZOTAC GeForce RTX 2060 Super AMP Extreme 8GB GDDR6 Gaming Graphics Card', 'ZOTAC GeForce RTX 2060 Super AMP Extreme 8GB GDDR6 Gaming Graphics Card', '<p>Based on the Turing architecture, the&nbsp;<strong>ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX 2060 SUPER AMP Extreme Graphics Card</strong>&nbsp;brings the power of real-time ray tracing and AI to your PC games.</p>\n\n<p>The front panel of the card features a variety of outputs. There are three DisplayPort outputs and one HDMI 2.0 output. The RTX 2060 SUPER is not just about high-resolution gaming. Computationally intensive programs can utilize the GPU&#39;s 2176 cores to accelerate tasks using CUDA or other APIs.</p>\n\n<p>For cooling, ZOTAC implemented IceStorm 2.0 cooling. It utilizes dual 8mm wide copper heatpipes to maximize heat extraction from the core while the aluminum fin array disperses heat. It is also mounted with triple 90mm fans that amplify airflow and reduce noise.</p>\n', '', 'zotac-geforce-rtx-2060-super-amp-extreme-8gb-gddr6-gaming-graphics-card', 6, 104, '0', '0', 48, '<p>Based on the Turing architecture, the&nbsp;<strong>ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX 2060 SUPER AMP Extreme Graphics Card</strong>&nbsp;brings the power of real-time ray tracing and AI to your PC games.</p>\n\n<p>The front panel of the card features a variety of outputs. There are three DisplayPort outputs and one HDMI 2.0 output. The RTX 2060 SUPER is not just about high-resolution gaming. Computationally intensive programs can utilize the GPU&#39;s 2176 cores to accelerate tasks using CUDA or other APIs.</p>\n\n<p>For cooling, ZOTAC implemented IceStorm 2.0 cooling. It utilizes dual 8mm wide copper heatpipes to maximize heat extraction from the core while the aluminum fin array disperses heat. It is also mounted with triple 90mm fans that amplify airflow and reduce noise.</p>\n', '', 'featured,new,hot,day', NULL, 'en', 'qPosVEmkn5MOQe3T9uhS1b7pZ', 0, '', '', '', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', '2020-07-08 07:16:21', '2020-07-08 07:16: