(917, 'Anker PowerCore III Sense 10K PD -Black Fabric', 'Anker PowerCore III Sense 10K PD -Black Fabric', '<ul>\n	<li><strong>High-Speed Charging</strong></li>\n	<li>The 18W Power Delivery USB-C port pumps out enough power to charge&nbsp;iPhone 11 Pro at full speed<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Portable Power: PowerCore III Sense 10K is one of our slimmest Power Delivery power banks yet, with enough capacity to provide more than two charges for iPhone XS or Google Pixel, and almost one full charge for an 11&rdquo; iPad Pro.</li>\n	<li>Triple Charging Modes: 18W Power Delivery USB-C port, PowerIQ-enabled USB-A port, and trickle-charging mode for low-power devices. Use the dual USB ports to charge two devices simultaneously.</li>\n	<li>Rapid Recharge: Power up your PowerCore in just 4.5 hours with a USB-C Power Delivery wall charger (not included). Recharging via USB-A charger and cable (not included) will take approximately 10.2 hours.</li>\n</ul>\n', ' ', 'anker-powercore-iii-sense-10k-pd--black-fabric', 2, 26, '0', '0', 21, '<ul>\n	<li><strong>High-Speed Charging</strong></li>\n	<li>The 18W Power Delivery USB-C port pumps out enough power to charge&nbsp;iPhone 11 Pro at full speed<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Portable Power: PowerCore III Sense 10K is one of our slimmest Power Delivery power banks yet, with enough capacity to provide more than two charges for iPhone XS or Google Pixel, and almost one full charge for an 11&rdquo; iPad Pro.</li>\n	<li>Triple Charging Modes: 18W Power Delivery USB-C port, PowerIQ-enabled USB-A port, and trickle-charging mode for low-power devices. Use the dual USB ports to charge two devices simultaneously.</li>\n	<li>Rapid Recharge: Power up your PowerCore in just 4.5 hours with a USB-C Power Delivery wall charger (not included). Recharging via USB-A charger and cable (not included) will take approximately 10.2 hours.</li>\n</ul>\n', ' ', 'featured,new,hot,day', NULL, 'en', 'tCNPRoeSyE1U3GY5qDTAn6mfb', 0, '', ' ', ' ', 1, '', NULL, '', 0, '